  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA203-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉākat tōḻi colli (ET: talaimakaṭkuc coḷḷuvāḷāy) varaivu kaṭāyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante urged for marriage, speaking when HE was behind the fence.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA203">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            muḻaṅkutirai keḻīiya mūri yekkart</l>
<l>            taṭantāṭ ṭāḻai muḷḷuṭai neṭuntōṭ</l>
<l>            ṭakamaṭaṟ potuḷiya mukaimutir vāṉpūṅ</l>
<l>            kōṭuvārn taṉṉa veṇpūt tāḻai</l>
<l>            yeṟitirai yutaittaliṟ poṅkit tātucōrpu </l>
<l>            ciṟukkuṭip pākkattu maṟukupulā maṟukku</l>
<l>            maṇaṅkamaḻ kāṉa liyaintanaṅ kēṇmai</l>
<l>            yorunāḷ piriyiṉu muyvari teṉṉātu</l>
<l>            kataḻpari neṭuntēr varavāṇ ṭaḻuṅkac</l>
<l>            ceytataṉ ṟappa laṉṟiyu </l>
<l>            muyavuppuṇarn taṉṟiv vaḻuṅka lūrē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Without considering that escaping is difficult,</l>
<l rend="indent4">even if separated [just] for one day,</l>
<l rend="indent">from our intimacy that was enjoyable in the seashore-grove</l>
<l rend="indent">fragrant with scent,</l>
<l rend="indent2">where the white flowers of the Tāḻai tree, like upright conches,</l>
<l rend="indent2">sky flowers ripening from buds that were dense [between] the inner fronds</l>
<l rend="indent3">in thorny long masses on the broad-trunked Tāḻai tree</l>
<l rend="indent3">in the great dunes that were full of thundering waves,</l>
<l rend="indent2">[their] pollen dripping down as the dashing waves foam while striking,<note place="foot">Here syntax and meaning are unmarked and far from clear. The first lines, too, with this double <term xml:lang="ta">tāḻai</term> and double <term xml:lang="ta">pū</term>, look somewhat suspicious.</note></l>
<l rend="indent2">defy the stench of fish in the streets of the village with small homes,</l>
<l>and apart from the mistake it committed</l>
<l rend="indent4">to spoil the coming there of the long chariot of hasty motion,</l>
<l>this noisy village is united in suffering.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
